OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778223659
OL,3,CManchester City win first WSL title in
OL,4,Cdecade
OL,6,FManchester City were crowned Women's
OL,7,FSuper League champions for the first
OL,8,Ftime since 2016 after Arsenal were
OL,9,Fheld to a 1-1 draw at Brighton.
OL,11,FThird-placed Arsenal were eager to
OL,12,Fbounce back from Saturday's Champions
OL,13,FLeague exit to Lyon and keep the title
OL,14,Frace alive in the first of three
OL,15,Fmatches in hand on City.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
