PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778223659
OL,3,CManchester City win first WSL title in
OL,4,Cdecade
OL,6,FArsenal and boss Renee Slegers were
OL,7,Fwell aware only victory at Brighton
OL,8,Fwould be enough and despite Frida
OL,9,FMaanum's 62nd-minute strike being able
OL,10,Fto cancel out Fuka Tsunoda's first-
OL,11,Fhalf opener for Brighton, the visitors
OL,12,Fcould not find a winner and it ensured
OL,13,FCity were able to celebrate silverware
OL,14,Fin their first season under boss
OL,15,FAndree Jeglertz.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
