FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778223659
OL,3,CManchester City win first WSL title in
OL,4,Cdecade
OL,6,FArsenal had to settle for a 1-1 draw
OL,7,Fat Broadfield Stadium which signalled
OL,8,Fthe end of their title challenge and
OL,9,FChelsea's run of six consecutive
OL,10,Fleague championships on a special
OL,11,Fnight for champions City.
OL,13,FBrighton stunned the visitors in the
OL,14,F43rd-minute when (Fuka) Tsunoda beat
OL,15,FVictoria Pelova to the ball and
OL,16,Fdrilled beyond Daphne van Domselaar
OL,17,Fvia a deflection.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
