PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778223659
OL,3,CManchester City win first WSL title in
OL,4,Cdecade
OL,6,FPelova was withdrawn at half-time and
OL,7,FArsenal returned with better intent
OL,8,Fwith Russo only able to scuff wide
OL,9,Fbefore Foord forced Chiamaka Nnadozie
OL,10,Fto tip over.
OL,12,FMaanum had penalty appeals waved away
OL,13,Fsoon after before the leveller arrived
OL,14,Fwith 62 minutes played.
OL,16,FRusso brilliantly spun away and played
OL,17,Finto Maanum, who composed herself and
OL,18,Fslotted into the bottom corner, but
OL,19,FSlegers still produced a triple
OL,20,Fsubstitution Katie McCabe, Beth Mead
OL,21,Fand Stina Blackstenius sent on.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
