PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778223659
OL,3,CManchester City win first WSL title in
OL,4,Cdecade
OL,6,FA final roll of the dice was the
OL,7,Fintroduction of Chloe Kelly with seven
OL,8,Fminutes left, but the former
OL,9,FManchester City winger was unable to
OL,10,Fproduce any late magic to deny her old
OL,11,Fside.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
